xpad|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
xpad: xpad (A note application)
xpad:
xpad: xpad is a sticky note application written using GTK+ 2.0 that strives
xpad: to be simple, fault-tolerant, and customizable. xpad consists of
xpad: independent pad windows; each is basically a text box in which notes
xpad: can be written. Despite being called xpad, all that is needed to run
xpad: or compile it is the GTK+ 2.0 libraries.
xpad:
xpad: http://xpad.sourceforge.net/
xpad:
xpad: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
